{"claim_id": "claim_032", "text": "In the example, 5 MS2 spectra were associated with the candidate chromatographic peak.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "There are 5 MS2 spectra representing fragmentation of the ion(s) measured\nin our candidate chromatographic peak.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_xcms/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [39978, 40090], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "data", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000006", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": null, "spine_entity_ids": ["spectra_package"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_033", "text": "The combineSpectra method can reduce multiple fragment spectra into a single consensus spectrum.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "We next reduce this to a single MS2\nspectrum using the `combineSpectra()` method", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_xcms/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [40091, 40171], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": null, "spine_entity_ids": ["spectra_package"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_034", "text": "combinePeaks combines mass peaks from input spectra with m/z differences smaller than 20 ppm into one peak.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "Mass peaks from all input spectra with a difference in m/z smaller 20 ppm\n(parameter `ppm`) were combined into one peak", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_xcms/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [40909, 41028], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": null, "spine_entity_ids": ["spectra_package"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_035", "text": "With minProp parameter set to 0.8, the resulting spectrum contains only peaks present in 80% of input spectra.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "Due to parameter `minProp = 0.8`, the resulting MS2\nspectrum contains only peaks that were present in 80% of the input spectra.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_xcms/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [41085, 41212], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "data", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000006", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": null, "spine_entity_ids": ["spectra_package"]}
